OL,3,CGraffiti in Belfast investigated as
OL,4,C'racially motivated hate crime'
OL,6,FGraffiti which appeared in Belfast is
OL,7,Fbeing investigated as racially
OL,8,Fmotivated hate crime.
OL,10,FThe daubings, which appeared in the
OL,11,Fsouth of the city earlier this week,
OL,12,Ftargeted the French rape survivor and
OL,13,Factivist, Gisele Pelicot, and also
OL,14,Fcontained racial slurs against other
OL,15,Fethnicities.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
