OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784211519
OL,3,CGraffiti in Belfast investigated as
OL,4,C'racially motivated hate crime'
OL,6,FMs Pelicot's ex-husband, Dominique
OL,7,FPelicot, was jailed for 20 years for
OL,8,Fdrugging and raping her and allowing
OL,9,Fother men to rape her while she was
OL,10,Funconscious, in abuse that lasted
OL,11,Fnearly a decade.
OL,13,FA Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,14,F(PSNI) spokesperson said they are
OL,15,Finvestigating a report of graffiti
OL,16,Fpainted in a number of locations in
OL,17,Fthe Sandy Row area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
