PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784211519
OL,3,CGraffiti in Belfast investigated as
OL,4,C'racially motivated hate crime'
OL,6,FThey said the graffiti contained a
OL,7,Fnumber of "extremely offensive racist
OL,8,Fand misogynistic terms", and was
OL,9,Freported to police on Tuesday July 14.
OL,11,F"Although this has since been painted
OL,12,Fover, our investigation into this
OL,13,Freport of criminal damage continues
OL,14,Fand we are treating the graffiti as a
OL,15,Fracially motivated hate crime," they
OL,16,Fsaid.
