OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784211519
OL,3,CGraffiti in Belfast investigated as
OL,4,C'racially motivated hate crime'
OL,6,F"There is no place in our society for
OL,7,Fthis type of intimidating behaviour
OL,8,Fand we will continue to engage with
OL,9,Flocal representatives and partner
OL,10,Fagencies around community safety.
OL,12,F"We know the people of south Belfast
OL,13,Fwill rightly condemn this disgraceful
OL,14,Fattack."
OL,16,FThey added an appeal for information.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@HO]
