OL,3,CGraffiti in Belfast investigated as
OL,4,C'racially motivated hate crime'
OL,6,F"We would appeal to anyone who noticed
OL,7,Fanything suspicious in the area, or
OL,8,Fwho may have relevant doorbell camera,
OL,9,FCCTV, or other footage, to contact
OL,10,Fpolice on 101 quoting reference number
OL,11,F649 of 14/07/26," they said.
OL,13,F"Reports can also be made online at
OL,14,Fpsni.police.uk/report or in confidence
OL,15,Fthrough Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111."
